This branch is a response to Issue 317 on the official XCSoar Github. See
https://github.com/XCSoar/XCSoar/issues/317

To build kernel:

cd ${KOBOSRC}
make mrproper
cp ${XCSOAR}/kobo/kernel/N249.config ${KOBOSRC}/.config
make -j3 ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-kobo-linux-gnueabihf- zImage ; echo $?
sudo dd if=./arch/arm/boot/zImage of=/dev/${SDCARD} bs=512 seek=2048 ; sync ; sync
